<div id="c1">
<p>I too enjoyed the NPR/This American Life &#8220;The Global Pool of Money&#8221; programme.   But, there has been plenty of good coverage in the press if you chose to look.  See e.g. http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2008/apr/08/creditcrunch.banking .</p>

<p>And I&#8217;m not so sure that the news is broken.  The decline in sales is probably indicative of some other wider (societal) issue.</p>

