<div id="c2">
<p>That article conveys far less information and is a lot less readable than the <em>TAL</em> piece. It&#8217;s a pretty standard long newspaper feature and I can&#8217;t imagine the average person understanding the situation from it or even getting thru it. (Compare Susan Faludi&#8217;s introduction to her book <em>Backlash</em> to her newspaper article on LBOs and you&#8217;ll see how impossible it is to do good work in that format.)</p>

